Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.81,1:33:07.67,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还不死心
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.80,1:33:09.27,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 是真的啊
